ORDER
The petition for writ of certiorari is denied.
The partial stay entered in this matter on March 4, 1982 is vacated.

attorneys: Alfred Factor, Kirshenbaum & Kirshen-baum, Providence, for plaintiff-respondent.
Leonard A. Kamaras, Providence, for defendant-petitioner.
